parse.title: List of heads of state and government who survived assassination attempts

text.*:
This article is an orphan, as no other articles link to it. Please introduce links to this page from related articles; try the Find link tool for suggestions. (September 2017)

This article is a list of heads of state who have survived assassination attempts. Many notable heads of government have been survivors of unsuccessful assassination attempts.

Contents

  • 1 List
  • 2 Gallery
  • 3 See also
  • 4 Notes and references
